{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cd395671-606f-4f93-b454-406043b4a28d","content":"Yes, you'll hit compatibility issues. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Framework support dropped in MSTest v3:**\n| Target | MSTest v3 Support |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped |\n\nMSTest v3 requires **.NET 6.0+** for .NET (Core) targets. Both `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` are out of support and not compatible.\n\n**To migrate, you'd need to:**\n1. Replace `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` with `net6.0` or later (ideally `net8.0`).\n2. Replace the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages with the unified **`MSTest`** meta-package (v3+).\n\nWould you like me to update the project file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1062d4a3-47f7-4d35-a08c-2cc9807d776e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user's project targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3.\n\nMSTest v3 dropped support for older frameworks. Let me think about what I know:\n\n- MSTest v3 requires at minimum .NET 6.0+ for .NET (Core) targets, and .NET Framework 4.6.2+ for .NET Framework targets.\n- Actually, let me be more precise. MSTest v3 (the MSTest meta-package or MSTest.TestFramework 3.x) dropped support for:\n  - .NET 5.0 (which is already out of support)\n  - .NET Core 3.1 (also out of support)\n  - .NET Framework 4.6.2 is still supported\n\nSo the user will run into compatibility issues with `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` since MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0 or higher for those targets.  They'd need to upgrade to at least `net6.0`, ideally `net8.0` since .NET 6 is approaching end of support. The `net462` target should work fine. I should also mention that MSTest v3 consolidates the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages into a single `MSTest` package, though the older separate packages still work.","outputTokens":686,"requestId":"5C27:13A49B:490BCF:5AA8BD:69F562F5"},"id":"cc8056cb-13d9-4f8d-a807-d57f23f0809b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:35:47.344Z","parentId":"390a758c-c73f-4cdb-82b5-2000740f717a"}
